  "bench_knowledge": [
    "PFA dissolves to release formaldehyde, an IARC Group 1 (known) human carcinogen and respiratory sensitiser. Even brief vapour exposure during preparation is a documented occupational hazard. Fresh preparation from powder in PBS (rather than from stored 16% stock solutions) provides better morphological preservation and avoids formate contamination that accumulates in aged solutions."
